To verify, please read <#605188295613349888> or talk to a <@&605188129174847488>.

- Higher ranking in the online user list.
- Allowed to post your Selfies in Verified Selfie Channels.
- You will get the <@&605187926120333484> role instead of <@&605187907229188151>.
- A <@&605187926120333484> Profile Badge. For more info, check <#609195786554834964>.
- Extra credibility. Everyone will know you have proven your identity.
- 8 Extra colors for your name: <:Verified1:606774509134938119> <:Verified2:606774509466550292> <:Verified3:606774509445316609> <:Verified4:606774509558693901> <:Verified5:606774509353304075> <:Verified6:606774509642579980> <:Verified7:606774509500104715> <:Verified8:606774509365624833>.
